title: Cleaning and Stain Removal for Dummies
description:
Cleaning and Stain Removal for Dummies by Gill Chilton

Overview: The everyday science of cleaning up your act.
This book will help lessen the grind of daily cleaning and accidental spills. Inside you'll find an easy-to-follow section on stain removal and a room-by-room guide to buffing up everything from curtains to carpets to cars. With practical shortcuts designed to reduce the amount of time you spend cleaning, this friendly guide offers fresh ways to keep your home and your possessions looking immaculate.

Discover how to:

Clean and care for your clothes.
Cut down on specialist cleaning bills
Maintain your home inside and out
Put together a stain removal kit
